    <h1>HTML &lt;p&gt; Tag</h1>
    <p>
        HTML tag defines the paragraph and is used to give structure to text content within a webpage. It is a
        block-level
        element & used to add the space or margins after and before the element this is done by browsers by default.
    </p>
    <p>
        Note: The HTML
        tag supports the Global Attributes and Event Attributes.
    </p>
